PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F359A1664752882
OL,5,FBBC Two trade test transmissions were
OL,6,Fseverely curtailed and the transmitters
OL,7,Fwere left off for much of the daytime.
OL,8,FIt was annoying to the trade as it made
OL,9,Fit harder to install TVs and aerials
OL,10,Fbut amongst the wider public only
OL,11,Fhardcore fans of the test card would
OL,12,Fhave been disappointed.
OL,14,FThe move was only formally reversed in
OL,15,F1983 at the same time as schools
OL,16,Fprogrammes moved to BBC Two.
OL,18,FSo would transmitter shutdowns now be
OL,19,Fan option? I would suggest this is
OL,20,Fhighly unlikely.
OL,3,CEnergy price crisis: time to review
OL,4,Ctransmitter usage?
OL,22,                                   G2/6
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
