SC,0003
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F359A1664752882
OL,5,FObviously daytime shutdowns are now out
OL,6,Fof the question. Because several
OL,7,Fchannels are broadcast on the same
OL,8,Fmultiplex, it makes no difference when
OL,9,Fan individual channel like BBC Three or
OL,10,FFour is off air.
OL,12,FIf there were to be any benefit in
OL,13,Fswitching off transmitters in the
OL,14,Fmiddle of the night, all the services
OL,15,Fon a particular multiplex would need to
OL,16,Fshut down.
OL,18,FCould anyone really envisage all BBC
OL,19,Fservices being off air, say, from 1am
OL,20,Fto 6am?
OL,3,CEnergy price crisis: time to review
OL,4,Ctransmitter usage?
OL,22,                                   G3/6
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
