PN,35904
SC,0004
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F359A1664752882
OL,5,FThe BBC would not want to provide
OL,6,Fdifferent levels of service on
OL,7,Fdifferent platforms  satellite, cable
OL,8,Fand online streaming would have to stop
OL,9,Ftoo.
OL,11,FBecause the BBC no longer owns or
OL,12,Foperates the transmitter network, it is
OL,13,Fno longer directly responsible for the
OL,14,Felectricity costs either.
OL,16,FSo while dramatic action can be ruled
OL,17,Fout, is it worth an audit to see if the
OL,18,Fcurrent transmitter network is fully
OL,19,Fnecessary?
OL,3,CEnergy price crisis: time to review
OL,4,Ctransmitter usage?
