OL,5,FSome small relay transmitters were
OL,6,Fbuilt to deal with localised analogue
OL,7,Freception problems  bad ghosting from
OL,8,Ftall buildings or dips in the signal
OL,9,Fquality.
OL,11,FIt may be possible that Freeview
OL,12,Freception from the main transmitter in
OL,13,Fthese areas is perfectly adequate even
OL,14,Fif analogue reception was compromised.
OL,16,FThe exact numbers who actuality rely on
OL,17,Frelay transmitters now  as opposed to
OL,18,Fthe number of homes they cover  is not
OL,19,Fclear.
OL,3,CEnergy price crisis: time to review
OL,4,Ctransmitter usage?
