PN,35906
SC,0006
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F359A1664752882
OL,5,FSo even if those who predict the end of
OL,6,Fterrestrial television are letting
OL,7,Ftheir imaginations run riot, maybe it
OL,8,Fis time to audit the relays.
OL,10,FStill, if any were to prove unnecessary
OL,11,Fthere would need to be proper notice
OL,12,Fgiven to viewers. Help with alternative
OL,13,Fmeans of reception would need to be
OL,14,Foffered.
OL,16,FIt might be the right thing to do to
OL,17,Fensure the transmitter network is as
OL,18,Fefficient as possible. But it would not
OL,19,Fhelp with the immediate problem of
OL,20,Fdramatic energy price rises.
OL,3,CEnergy price crisis: time to review
